								<foliation>
									<p>211 folios (+ 2 modern paper flyleaves at the beginning and at the end). </p>
								</foliation>
								<collation>
									<p>21 quires: ii-xx10 (folios 12-200); xxi7 (201-208). Folios 1-11 and 209-211 contain various fragments, partly belonging to the original manuscript, and supply a deficiency in the text.</p>
									<p>Quires signed with Hebrew letters and Arabic numerals at the end.</p>
								</collation>
