						<additions>
							<p>A note of sale: folio 1r.</p>
							<p>Folio 2r: contains a document, partly in a Scriptural language, in which a certain Benyamin ben Avraham of Aden is recommended  to the charity of the cities of Yemen. Cf similar documents in Cairo Genizah.</p>
